modName: AZ Argonian Vampire No Color Change
summary: When your argonian character becomes a vampire their skin color no longer changes. The teeth still change but you no longer become an ugly pale color.
descriptionHtml:
When your argonian character becomes a vampire their skin color no longer changes. The teeth still change but you no longer become an ugly pale color.

Place as close to last as possible in Load Order.

Khajiit Version
http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/23280
author: Aurin Zalas
